(15, 'bronchoscopy', 'bronchoscopy', 'bron321', 3, '56.00', 'Yes', '50.00', '28', 'Image result for bronchoscopymedlineplus.gov\r\nA bronchoscopy is a procedure that allows a doctor to examine the inside of the lungs, including the bronchi, which are the main pathways into the lungs. During a bronchoscopy, a doctor inserts a thin tube containing a light and camera into the lungs through the nose or mouth', '7572d9b9f68ecb185a3ebaccef551b59.png', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=bronchoscopy&amp;tbm=isch&amp;source=iu&amp;ictx=1&amp;fir=im7PEdFkzYJYmM%253A%252Cao-RBxzRLpLIyM%252C_&amp;vet=1&amp;usg=AI4_-kTjhTNY_PKCcbQGaz-_FQp1fzvW5g&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjGotu_ronlAhXKKFAKHUaVDZsQ9QEwAHoECAMQAw#imgrc=im7PEdFkzYJYmM:\">medlineplus.gov</a></p>\n\n<p>A&nbsp;<strong>bronchoscopy</strong>&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;procedure&nbsp;that&nbsp;allows&nbsp;a&nbsp;doctor&nbsp;to&nbsp;examine&nbsp;the&nbsp;inside&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;lungs,&nbsp;including&nbsp;the&nbsp;bronchi,&nbsp;which&nbsp;are&nbsp;the&nbsp;main&nbsp;pathways&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;lungs.&nbsp;During&nbsp;a&nbsp;<strong>bronchoscopy</strong>,&nbsp;a&nbsp;doctor&nbsp;inserts&nbsp;a&nbsp;thin&nbsp;tube&nbsp;containing&nbsp;a&nbsp;light&nbsp;and&nbsp;camera&nbsp;into&nbsp;the&nbsp;lungs&nbsp;through&nbsp;the&nbsp;nose&nbsp;or&nbsp;mouth</p>\n', '', 2, '<ul>\n	<li>breathing&nbsp;difficulties.</li>\n	<li>chest&nbsp;pain.</li>\n	<li>coughing&nbsp;up&nbsp;blood.</li>\n	<li>fever.</li>\n	<li>a&nbsp;rapid&nbsp;heart&nbsp;rate.</li>\n</ul>\n', 'Result 1', 0, 'Yes', '', '', 'Test', 'Active', 'No', 0, 0, '', '', '2019-10-07 05:19:28', '2019-10-07 05:19:28', 13),
